Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 艾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界…外面的世界真的很廣闊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全看不到另一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過艾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在所看到的不過是世界的冰山一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
